-new-crush-of-internet-whos-she/|title=Girl Dancing on Left Side on 'Bohot Hard' is The New Crush of Internet, Who's She?|date=2019-02-25|website=PagalParrot|language=en-US|access-date=17 May 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.shethepeople.tv/news/tiktok-app-women-stars-india|title=Meet The Sensational Women TikTok Stars In India|last=Das|first=Ria|date=17 April 2019|website=SheThePeople TV|language=en-US|access-date=17 May 2019}}</ref> Many celebrities such as [[Deven Shahane]], [[Varun Dhawan]], [[Sanya Malhotra]] and [[Sherlyn Chopra]] have been seen dancing to the hit song.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment/news/people/article/video-alert-dangal-girl-sanya-malhotra-burns-the-dance-floor-fans-say-boht-hard/416716|title=Video Alert! Dangal girl Sanya Malhotra burns the dance floor, fans say, 'Boht Hard' {{!}} Entertainment News|website=www.timesnownews.com|language=en-GB|access-date=17 May 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsx.com/entertainment/sanya-malhotra-dance-video-dangal-girl-puts-on-her-dancing-shoes-for-machayenge|title=Sanya Malhotra dance video: Dangal girl puts on her dancing shoes for Machayenge|date=2019-05-11|website=NewsX|language=en|access-date=17 May 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.india.com/buzz/bollywood-hottie-sherlyn-chopra-flaunts-her-sexy-curves-as-she-groves-to-emiways-machayenge-in-post-workout-video-3623818/|title=Sherlyn Chopra Flaunts Her Curves as She Groves to Emiway's 'Machayenge' in Post-workout Video|date=7 April 2019|website=India.com|language=en|access-date=17 May 2019}}</ref> Machayenge was covered by Indian actor [[Ranveer Singh]] on [[Filmfare Awards|Filmfare 2019]].{{Citation needed|date=May 2019}} The music video reached more than 165 million views on [[YouTube]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dbase.tube/v/7tNPxY_ntEA|title=Statistical Insights / EMIWAY- MACHAYENGE (PROD BY.TONY JAMES)|website=Dbase.tube}}</ref> Machayenge is one of Bantai's most popular songs.\n\nTh